Add `opentelemetry-instrumentation-transformers`, instrumenting local
HuggingFace `transformers` text-generation pipelines
(`TextGenerationPipeline.__call__`), emitting standard GenAI semantic
conventions (`gen_ai.*`) via `opentelemetry-util-genai`. Local inference
exposes no token usage or finish reason, so those fields are omitted. Requires
`OTEL_SEMCONV_STABILITY_OPT_IN=gen_ai_latest_experimental`.
